But it's also the exact mechanic of how an artificial intelligence language model starts hallucinating fake facts.

01:42.480 --> 01:42.540
Yeah.

01:42.640 --> 01:46.060
It is how a stem cell inside a human embryo survives.

01:46.340 --> 01:53.940
And incredibly, it is how you, the listener, are actively forming concepts in your brain to understand the very words I'm saying to you right now.

01:54.020 --> 01:58.740
We are looking at a fundamental claim about how reality basically stabilizes itself.

01:58.880 --> 01:59.040
Yeah.

01:59.040 --> 02:01.900
Usually we compartmentalize the world.

02:02.060 --> 02:05.260
We give physicists a manual full of equations for quantum fields.

02:05.860 --> 02:05.980
Right.

02:06.160 --> 02:10.720
