47:30.560 --> 47:32.420
Four totally different mechanisms.

47:32.740 --> 47:33.740
But here's the trick, right?

47:34.240 --> 47:38.980
All four of those theories perfectly fit the historical data from 1970 to 2020.

47:39.200 --> 47:39.640
Exactly.

47:39.840 --> 47:42.540
If you look at the past, they all look completely correct.

47:42.720 --> 47:45.460
