01:01:33.080 --> 01:01:39.200
And remember, as Flyxion is deeply careful to point out, this is not a proven, finalized universal law yet.

01:01:39.300 --> 01:01:40.600
Right. It's an operational schema.

01:01:41.000 --> 01:01:42.120
It is a new lens.

01:01:42.720 --> 01:01:46.440
It gives you, the listener, a powerful cognitive tool.

