Under the admissibility principle, these are not just objects.

01:02:34.120 --> 01:02:35.760
They are trajectory stabilizers.

01:02:35.960 --> 01:02:41.460
They are the massive, macro-scale constraint membranes that preserve the admissibility of human society.

